WEBVTT

00:00:10.600 --> 00:00:12.000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

00:01:06.540 --> 00:01:08.000
[The Eternal Fragrance]

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:11.980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

00:01:12.020 --> 00:01:15.140
[Episode 23]

00:01:17.470 --> 00:01:21.420
You're the maid who took Jingwu away!

00:01:24.160 --> 00:01:26.220
I'm Miaoqing. Greetings, Your Ladyship.

00:01:28.910 --> 00:01:31.860
Insulting nobility is punishable by death.

00:01:32.880 --> 00:01:33.860
Drag her off and flog her to death.

00:01:33.880 --> 00:01:34.290
- Yes. - Yes.

00:01:34.310 --> 00:01:34.860
Wait!

00:01:40.080 --> 00:01:40.620
Tongzhou.

00:01:44.830 --> 00:01:45.500
Everyone leave.

00:01:46.310 --> 00:01:46.780
- Yes. - Yes.

00:01:51.240 --> 00:01:51.810
Tongzhou.

00:01:52.470 --> 00:01:54.140
This lowly maid has no sense of rank.

00:01:54.520 --> 00:01:55.530
Why keep her around?

00:01:57.550 --> 00:01:58.530
Without her,

00:01:59.110 --> 00:02:01.370
Jingwu would've fallen into Zong Quan's hands too.

00:02:08.360 --> 00:02:10.090
Miaoqing, take the Crown Prince away.

00:02:11.030 --> 00:02:12.620
Yes, Your Highness.

00:02:23.990 --> 00:02:24.570
Tongzhou.

00:02:26.710 --> 00:02:27.410
Tongzhou.

00:02:28.110 --> 00:02:29.740
Look.

00:02:30.590 --> 00:02:31.940
Aren't these Twin Orbs beautiful?

00:02:35.900 --> 00:02:39.060
I've waited so long for this day.

00:02:39.360 --> 00:02:41.530
Do you remember when I first came to Duantu?

00:02:41.960 --> 00:02:43.940
You taught me calligraphy at Orchid Pavilion

00:02:44.480 --> 00:02:45.850
And said my writing was nice.

00:02:46.270 --> 00:02:49.740
You said I'd meet a good man

00:02:50.110 --> 00:02:50.970
And be happy forever.

00:02:53.760 --> 00:02:54.340
Tongzhou,

00:02:54.990 --> 00:02:56.940
You're the only man I've ever wanted.

00:02:57.800 --> 00:02:59.370
These Twin Orbs were left by my parents.

00:03:00.710 --> 00:03:02.780
In a few days, we'll be wed.

00:03:03.430 --> 00:03:04.090
I've decided.

00:03:04.670 --> 00:03:08.130
One orb will go on my crown.

00:03:08.360 --> 00:03:09.570
As for the other, I can...

00:03:09.590 --> 00:03:10.900
The Crown Prince ascends in three days.

00:03:13.150 --> 00:03:14.180
You want to be the Empress?

00:03:15.360 --> 00:03:17.530
I doubt Tonghe would approve from the grave.

00:03:20.900 --> 00:03:22.060
Jingwu is ascending the throne?

00:03:23.320 --> 00:03:24.570
Why not you, Tongzhou?

00:03:31.110 --> 00:03:32.250
It's okay.

00:03:32.960 --> 00:03:34.740
It's perfectly fine if you don't want to be

00:03:35.150 --> 00:03:36.970
The Emperor. I don't want to be the Empress.

00:03:37.480 --> 00:03:38.740
Just being with you

00:03:39.080 --> 00:03:40.130
Is enough for me.

00:03:44.320 --> 00:03:44.850
Lanya.

00:03:46.760 --> 00:03:48.410
When did you become so foolish?

00:03:51.390 --> 00:03:53.300
A blood debt can only be paid with blood.

00:03:54.150 --> 00:03:55.780
Killing you wouldn't quench my hatred.

00:03:58.270 --> 00:03:59.300
How could I ever marry you?

00:04:00.390 --> 00:04:00.780
Tong...

00:04:01.800 --> 00:04:02.250
Tong...

00:04:02.670 --> 00:04:03.220
Tongzhou.

00:04:05.390 --> 00:04:07.370
But... but you said

00:04:08.040 --> 00:04:09.300
Once Zong Quan was dead,

00:04:10.110 --> 00:04:11.850
Everything from the past would be forgotten.

00:04:13.200 --> 00:04:14.690
And you know

00:04:15.710 --> 00:04:17.300
I...

00:04:17.520 --> 00:04:18.460
I love you.

00:04:18.670 --> 00:04:19.250
- Shut up! - For...

00:04:21.640 --> 00:04:23.370
All you care about is yourself!

00:04:23.790 --> 00:04:26.250
No, Tongzhou. That's not true.

00:04:27.320 --> 00:04:29.060
After your parents died for the kingdom,

00:04:30.590 --> 00:04:33.180
Tonghe and I always treated you like a sister.

00:04:34.000 --> 00:04:35.370
We showered you with care. But you?

00:04:35.960 --> 00:04:37.620
For your selfish gain,

00:04:37.640 --> 00:04:39.860
You betrayed the Yue State and killed my uncle.

00:04:40.230 --> 00:04:42.100
No. No.

00:04:42.120 --> 00:04:44.130
You're utterly disgusting.

00:04:44.830 --> 00:04:46.890
Tongzhou! No. Tongzhou.

00:04:47.390 --> 00:04:49.690
Have you forgotten? The Heartbound Gu.

00:04:50.830 --> 00:04:53.570
Don't forget, you have the Heartbound Gu inside you.

00:04:53.880 --> 00:04:55.860
You are stuck with me for life.

00:04:56.390 --> 00:04:57.370
If you didn't love me,

00:04:57.590 --> 00:04:59.570
Why... why would you have taken the Heartbound Gu,

00:04:59.590 --> 00:05:00.180
Right?

00:05:00.830 --> 00:05:01.450
Tongzhou.

00:05:02.270 --> 00:05:02.980
Am I right?

00:05:03.000 --> 00:05:03.540
Lanya.

00:05:04.790 --> 00:05:06.570
There's a heart-protecting herb from Miaojiang

00:05:07.270 --> 00:05:09.010
That can shield one's heart meridians

00:05:09.030 --> 00:05:10.100
When the gu burns.

00:05:10.120 --> 00:05:10.890
Didn't you know?

00:05:24.960 --> 00:05:26.690
Tongzhou. No.

00:05:27.760 --> 00:05:28.690
You'll die.

00:05:29.440 --> 00:05:31.010
I'd rather burn myself

00:05:33.030 --> 00:05:34.540
Than let you have your way.

00:05:34.560 --> 00:05:36.100
I'll die too! No!

00:05:38.960 --> 00:05:40.060
Don't, Tongzhou!

00:05:43.830 --> 00:05:44.690
Tongzhou.

00:05:46.030 --> 00:05:47.010
Tongzhou.

00:05:50.710 --> 00:05:51.690
Does that hurt?

00:05:53.960 --> 00:05:55.860
This isn't even a fraction

00:05:57.080 --> 00:05:59.130
Of what you've done!

00:06:01.710 --> 00:06:02.570
Tongzhou...

00:06:08.470 --> 00:06:11.740
Are you really going to kill me, Tongzhou?

00:06:38.710 --> 00:06:44.690
"What can I give to my beloved?"

00:06:48.080 --> 00:06:56.940
"Twin Orbs, hanging

00:07:04.640 --> 00:07:05.210
Together."

00:07:35.230 --> 00:07:35.940
No.

00:07:51.560 --> 00:07:52.100
Who's there?

00:07:52.440 --> 00:07:52.980
Your Highness.

00:07:53.680 --> 00:07:54.620
It's me, Miaoqing.

00:07:56.590 --> 00:07:57.130
Your Highness.

00:08:05.710 --> 00:08:06.540
Why are you here?

00:08:09.960 --> 00:08:13.180
Your Highness, did you have a nightmare?

00:08:19.030 --> 00:08:22.100
Dreams aren't real. Don't take them to heart.

00:08:27.640 --> 00:08:29.060
They also said dreams weren't real.

00:08:31.080 --> 00:08:32.330
But the Yue State fell.

00:08:33.590 --> 00:08:36.900
Tonghe was killed. My uncle died horribly.

00:08:39.590 --> 00:08:41.060
All of it came true.

00:08:42.160 --> 00:08:42.940
No.

00:08:45.040 --> 00:08:46.060
That's all in the past.

00:08:47.080 --> 00:08:48.450
Things will get better.

00:08:51.630 --> 00:08:55.300
No. They won't get better.

00:08:55.870 --> 00:08:57.060
They all left me.

00:08:58.470 --> 00:08:59.730
I'm the only one left.

00:09:01.160 --> 00:09:02.380
All alone.

00:09:05.470 --> 00:09:07.780
Your Highness, you're not alone.

00:09:09.590 --> 00:09:11.140
I'll always be by your side.

00:09:27.320 --> 00:09:29.330
Lu and I are heading back to Wanxian Sect to report.

00:09:29.920 --> 00:09:30.970
Next time we meet,

00:09:31.320 --> 00:09:33.060
It'll probably be when the Sea Calamity comes.

00:09:37.990 --> 00:09:40.020
Tongzhou, I have to go too.

00:09:40.920 --> 00:09:43.020
My master and seniors at Zhuiyu Peak are waiting for news.

00:09:43.630 --> 00:09:44.260
Besides,

00:09:44.630 --> 00:09:45.940
I still need to find my old master.

00:09:46.200 --> 00:09:47.140
I really shouldn't stay any longer.

00:09:47.470 --> 00:09:48.610
Lifei, stay a few more days.

00:09:48.800 --> 00:09:49.940
I can help you find your master.

00:09:50.710 --> 00:09:51.810
Lifei has decided to leave.

00:09:52.040 --> 00:09:53.810
We should respect her choice.

00:09:53.990 --> 00:09:54.490
You...

00:09:59.710 --> 00:10:01.260
Ji Tongzhou, are you insane?

00:10:04.060 --> 00:10:05.900
Tongzhou, what are you doing?

00:10:13.230 --> 00:10:14.540
Is this the mark of demonic possession?

00:10:22.590 --> 00:10:23.610
Brahma's Net?

00:10:38.300 --> 00:10:41.690
You ignorant fools! Hand over the Divine Tree!

00:10:50.510 --> 00:10:51.300
Elder Cuixuan,

00:10:51.980 --> 00:10:53.380
We just finished driving out the Wugou army.

00:10:54.060 --> 00:10:55.330
We don't know anything about any Divine Tree.

00:10:55.980 --> 00:10:58.660
The night before last, the Divine Tree's aura surged straight into the sky.

00:10:59.180 --> 00:11:01.970
And the source of that aura was right here.

00:11:08.220 --> 00:11:11.850
Back at Chufeng Academy, the Divine Tree's aura also appeared.

00:11:13.060 --> 00:11:15.610
All of this is connected to you people.

00:11:16.340 --> 00:11:18.490
Today, I'll personally find out

00:11:19.230 --> 00:11:21.610
Where the Divine Tree is!

00:11:41.180 --> 00:11:41.970
Sir,

00:11:42.180 --> 00:11:43.900
Zong Quan killed Elder Xuanshan

00:11:43.990 --> 00:11:45.330
And slaughtered everyone in Xingzheng Hall.

00:11:46.460 --> 00:11:48.180
We nearly lost our lives

00:11:48.460 --> 00:11:49.690
Defeating him.

00:11:50.680 --> 00:11:51.570
Now you're here

00:11:51.980 --> 00:11:53.090
Demanding some Divine Tree

00:11:53.830 --> 00:11:55.810
Instead of healing us.

00:11:56.680 --> 00:11:58.570
You're leaving us no way out.

00:12:01.510 --> 00:12:02.490
Elder Cuixuan!

00:12:04.230 --> 00:12:05.730
Where were you when the Yue State fell

00:12:06.590 --> 00:12:09.180
And Xingzheng Hall was wiped out?

00:12:09.820 --> 00:12:11.450
Where was Wuyue Court

00:12:11.680 --> 00:12:12.900
When we fought Zong Quan?

00:12:13.630 --> 00:12:16.300
Compared to the calamity that threatens to ruin the Central Plains,

00:12:17.100 --> 00:12:19.940
The fate of one kingdom means nothing.

00:12:20.470 --> 00:12:21.610
As for Zong Quan,

00:12:21.980 --> 00:12:24.490
He's fallen to demonic arts and has abandoned the immortal path.

00:12:24.870 --> 00:12:26.660
He has nothing to do with Wuyue Court!

00:12:27.510 --> 00:12:29.260
I suggest you see reason

00:12:29.630 --> 00:12:31.060
And hand over the Divine Tree.

00:12:31.830 --> 00:12:33.970
No more useless words.

00:12:34.320 --> 00:12:36.260
We really don't know where the Divine Tree is.

00:12:36.440 --> 00:12:37.260
What can we give you?

00:12:43.470 --> 00:12:44.780
You're a revered master of an immortal sect.

00:12:45.110 --> 00:12:46.450
Yet you hound disciples over something

00:12:46.750 --> 00:12:47.540
That may not even exist.

00:12:48.630 --> 00:12:49.940
Do you not fear losing the hearts of your people?

00:12:52.440 --> 00:12:53.570
There is no Divine Tree here.

00:12:54.040 --> 00:12:56.810
If Wuyue Court insists on bullying the weak,

00:12:57.110 --> 00:12:59.940
I will fight you to the death!

00:13:00.350 --> 00:13:04.610
Fight to the death!

00:13:07.960 --> 00:13:09.210
Ignorant fools.

00:13:10.440 --> 00:13:11.730
With you people?

00:13:16.700 --> 00:13:17.300
Cuixuan,

00:13:17.960 --> 00:13:20.570
We came here to find the Divine Tree,

00:13:20.870 --> 00:13:21.850
Not to fight.

00:13:22.510 --> 00:13:23.380
Isn't that right?

00:13:25.540 --> 00:13:29.020
Since Zong Quan once occupied this place,

00:13:29.630 --> 00:13:30.940
Could he have hidden

00:13:31.160 --> 00:13:33.570
The Divine Tree somewhere here?

00:13:35.440 --> 00:13:36.300
Have you done

00:13:36.320 --> 00:13:38.730
A thorough search?

00:13:40.280 --> 00:13:40.900
Sir,

00:13:41.440 --> 00:13:42.570
We've been busy cleaning up the mess,

00:13:42.830 --> 00:13:43.610
And we're all wounded.

00:13:44.080 --> 00:13:44.970
We haven't done a full search yet.

00:13:45.540 --> 00:13:48.020
See? There are still gaps.

00:13:52.470 --> 00:13:55.090
Cuixuan, the Sea Sect has just settled down.

00:13:55.350 --> 00:13:57.540
We can't afford more conflict within the Mountain Sect.

00:13:58.230 --> 00:14:00.260
If we let our fellow cultivators down,

00:14:00.510 --> 00:14:02.970
The demons will take advantage.

00:14:03.960 --> 00:14:06.970
Ji Tongzhou just lost his entire family.

00:14:07.630 --> 00:14:09.090
It's understandable

00:14:09.200 --> 00:14:10.380
He spoke out of turn.

00:14:11.350 --> 00:14:12.380
How about this?

00:14:12.710 --> 00:14:14.420
Let's give the young ones some time

00:14:15.040 --> 00:14:17.420
To find the Divine Tree.

00:14:18.440 --> 00:14:19.210
Is that acceptable?

00:14:26.350 --> 00:14:27.450
Cuixuan, you're wise.

00:14:29.560 --> 00:14:33.060
The Divine Tree concerns the safety of the Central Plains.

00:14:33.750 --> 00:14:36.140
Everyone here bears responsibility!

00:14:37.280 --> 00:14:39.180
I'll give you twenty-four hours...

00:14:46.110 --> 00:14:47.140
Twelve hours.

00:14:48.110 --> 00:14:49.380
You have twelve hours

00:14:49.960 --> 00:14:50.970
To hand over the Divine Tree!

00:14:51.350 --> 00:14:54.380
Or I'll take matters into my own hands!

00:15:10.160 --> 00:15:13.330
Alright. Your life isn't in danger,

00:15:13.590 --> 00:15:14.850
But your energy is unstable.

00:15:14.990 --> 00:15:17.140
You need to rest well during this time.

00:15:19.200 --> 00:15:20.020
Master,

00:15:21.830 --> 00:15:24.900
- my spirit aura... - I don't want to hear it.

00:15:25.990 --> 00:15:28.210
And I don't want to know.

00:15:29.230 --> 00:15:32.260
All I know is you're my disciple.

00:15:35.470 --> 00:15:37.090
So I have to say something.

00:15:37.630 --> 00:15:39.060
You've got some nerve.

00:15:39.350 --> 00:15:40.210
With your skill level,

00:15:40.230 --> 00:15:42.450
How could you go head-to-head with Zong Quan?

00:15:42.990 --> 00:15:44.020
Silly girl.

00:15:44.960 --> 00:15:46.690
Well, none of you sect elders

00:15:46.710 --> 00:15:47.610
Lifted a finger.

00:15:48.560 --> 00:15:50.380
I was just following your teachings

00:15:50.400 --> 00:15:52.060
To be discerning and sacrifice myself for what's right.

00:15:52.230 --> 00:15:53.570
I wasn't about to stand by

00:15:53.590 --> 00:15:54.610
And do nothing like you.

00:15:56.750 --> 00:15:59.140
We weren't standing by.

00:15:59.870 --> 00:16:01.210
The immortal sects aren't supposed to

00:16:01.230 --> 00:16:03.180
Interfere in disputes between kingdoms.

00:16:04.110 --> 00:16:04.690
And

00:16:05.560 --> 00:16:07.610
When exactly did I teach you to sacrifice yourself?

00:16:07.710 --> 00:16:10.090
I've always taught you to stay alive.

00:16:11.080 --> 00:16:12.730
I'm doing pretty well at that.

00:16:21.960 --> 00:16:22.420
Sir.

00:16:28.320 --> 00:16:29.180
You're just in time.

00:16:29.750 --> 00:16:30.850
I was going to find you.

00:16:31.750 --> 00:16:33.090
They say you're exceptionally gifted.

00:16:33.110 --> 00:16:34.330
Where exactly is this gift of yours?

00:16:34.960 --> 00:16:36.330
You've had my disciple for three months.

00:16:36.440 --> 00:16:37.570
Look at her now.

00:16:37.990 --> 00:16:38.850
She's broken and battered.

00:16:38.870 --> 00:16:40.810
Can you even protect anyone?

00:16:50.350 --> 00:16:51.140
Sir, you're right.

00:16:54.200 --> 00:16:56.420
I didn't protect her well.

00:17:01.870 --> 00:17:05.450
Is this the same defiant brat

00:17:05.470 --> 00:17:07.330
Guangwei used to complain about?

00:17:13.750 --> 00:17:14.860
I trained him.

00:17:15.960 --> 00:17:16.690
Impressive, right?

00:17:32.100 --> 00:17:33.940
Why do I feel so out of place

00:17:33.960 --> 00:17:35.140
And unwanted?

00:17:35.990 --> 00:17:37.900
So awkward. I'm leaving.

00:17:42.790 --> 00:17:43.770
Sir, let me see you out.

00:18:06.880 --> 00:18:08.010
In six hours,

00:18:08.160 --> 00:18:10.660
At first light, when the sun and moon meet,

00:18:10.990 --> 00:18:11.660
The Brahma's Net

00:18:11.680 --> 00:18:13.690
Will be at its weakest.

00:18:14.160 --> 00:18:16.380
I'll do everything I can to hold Cuixuan off.

00:18:18.960 --> 00:18:19.730
What do you mean?

00:18:20.400 --> 00:18:21.100
Take her away.

00:18:24.400 --> 00:18:25.450
Go far away.

00:18:26.710 --> 00:18:28.530
Never return to Wuyue Court.

00:18:30.440 --> 00:18:30.940
But...

00:18:41.270 --> 00:18:41.970
Sir.

00:18:50.310 --> 00:18:51.690
If we don't find the Divine Tree,

00:18:51.960 --> 00:18:53.820
Cuixuan won't let this go.

00:18:56.200 --> 00:18:57.860
Lu, have you ever seen the Divine Tree?

00:18:58.880 --> 00:19:01.900
Legend says it was born from the spirit energy of heaven and earth

00:19:02.600 --> 00:19:03.860
And grows on Divine Tree Island.

00:19:05.270 --> 00:19:06.580
But after the last Sea Calamity,

00:19:07.070 --> 00:19:07.970
It vanished without a trace.

00:19:09.960 --> 00:19:11.210
It hasn't been seen in centuries?

00:19:13.160 --> 00:19:14.690
Then who knows where the Divine Tree is?

00:19:15.160 --> 00:19:16.730
He's clearly making things impossible.

00:19:17.400 --> 00:19:18.660
The Yue State just ended one war,

00:19:19.710 --> 00:19:21.140
And now we're stuck with this mess.

00:19:21.470 --> 00:19:22.380
Sorry to drag everyone into this.

00:19:25.200 --> 00:19:25.860
Tongzhou.

00:19:27.880 --> 00:19:28.380
Here.

00:19:29.070 --> 00:19:30.490
I had some snacks made.

00:19:30.790 --> 00:19:31.340
Try some.

00:19:33.960 --> 00:19:34.380
Here.

00:19:35.710 --> 00:19:36.340
Tongzhou.

00:19:36.990 --> 00:19:38.380
Once the twelve hours are up,

00:19:38.550 --> 00:19:39.620
What's your plan?

00:19:43.680 --> 00:19:45.770
I've already had Mingli scour the entire area.

00:19:46.600 --> 00:19:47.580
If we find it, we find it.

00:19:48.400 --> 00:19:49.290
If not,

00:19:51.340 --> 00:19:52.420
I'll take full responsibility.

00:19:56.070 --> 00:19:56.900
You all

00:19:57.710 --> 00:19:58.820
Risked your lives to help me.

00:19:59.400 --> 00:20:01.450
No matter what, I'll make sure you're all safe.

00:20:02.790 --> 00:20:04.290
I came here to protect you.

00:20:04.440 --> 00:20:05.530
How could I let you face this alone?

00:20:06.200 --> 00:20:08.450
If it comes to it, we'll fight Cuixuan.

00:20:08.880 --> 00:20:09.770
We might not lose.

00:20:13.230 --> 00:20:15.010
Lu, as for you...

00:20:16.200 --> 00:20:18.210
Gelin's friends are my friends.

00:20:37.030 --> 00:20:37.970
Unless the barrier is lifted,

00:20:38.200 --> 00:20:39.820
Everyone inside the imperial palace is trapped.

00:20:40.510 --> 00:20:41.820
No one else should be dragged into this.

00:20:42.400 --> 00:20:43.290
When the barrier weakens,

00:20:44.100 --> 00:20:45.010
I'll draw Cuixuan away.

00:20:45.640 --> 00:20:46.770
You take Lifei and get out.

00:20:47.600 --> 00:20:48.140
No.

00:20:50.340 --> 00:20:51.210
You make it sound simple.

00:20:52.100 --> 00:20:53.210
Cuixuan is cunning and sly.

00:20:53.270 --> 00:20:54.180
How will you draw him away?

00:21:00.680 --> 00:21:02.010
Cuixuan wants the Divine Tree.

00:21:05.100 --> 00:21:05.860
Actually, the Divine Tree...

00:21:05.880 --> 00:21:07.050
The Divine Tree is on me.

00:21:25.510 --> 00:21:27.530
This is... the Divine Tree?

00:21:28.160 --> 00:21:28.770
Where did you get it?

00:21:30.160 --> 00:21:31.010
From the Outcast Tomb at White Cliff.

00:21:33.960 --> 00:21:35.530
I thought you destroyed it.

00:21:36.880 --> 00:21:39.620
At the time, I sensed its unusual spirit energy

00:21:40.100 --> 00:21:41.180
And brought it back to study.

00:21:42.840 --> 00:21:43.940
It was only when Cuixuan came

00:21:44.470 --> 00:21:46.770
That I realized it was actually the Divine Tree.

00:21:50.640 --> 00:21:52.140
Would handing it over to Cuixuan

00:21:53.100 --> 00:21:54.380
Draw him away?

00:22:00.400 --> 00:22:01.140
Absolutely not.

00:22:02.880 --> 00:22:04.900
That night, the Divine Tree's aura surged straight into the sky.

00:22:05.400 --> 00:22:06.530
He'll never believe it came

00:22:07.030 --> 00:22:08.210
From just a piece of bone.

00:22:08.710 --> 00:22:11.420
We need to find a way to end this once and for all.

00:22:12.710 --> 00:22:14.100
Then we'll make it impossible to prove.

00:22:14.710 --> 00:22:16.010
Blame it all on Zong Quan!

00:22:17.030 --> 00:22:17.940
I was thinking the same thing.

00:22:18.960 --> 00:22:20.210
We could use the demonic energy

00:22:20.920 --> 00:22:21.940
On the Altar of Heaven.

00:22:27.230 --> 00:22:29.900
But how do we make it impossible to prove?

00:22:36.790 --> 00:22:39.210
I'll disguise myself as Lifei. You play the demon.

00:22:41.230 --> 00:22:41.940
Stop right there.

00:22:42.340 --> 00:22:43.450
Do you think he's blind?

00:22:47.100 --> 00:22:49.340
I'm warning you two, don't take any risks.

00:22:50.470 --> 00:22:51.580
Let me think of something else.

00:23:00.710 --> 00:23:02.100
Can't go by air.

00:23:04.160 --> 00:23:05.010
What about underground?

00:23:23.340 --> 00:23:24.010
Water.

00:23:25.920 --> 00:23:27.010
What about going by water?

00:23:54.840 --> 00:23:55.730
What are you doing here?

00:23:58.400 --> 00:24:00.770
Your Highness, I want to share your burden.

00:24:02.070 --> 00:24:03.730
You're just a maid. What can you do?

00:24:04.230 --> 00:24:05.100
Take care of yourself.

00:24:08.030 --> 00:24:10.660
The late emperor and Elder Xuanshanzi entrusted you with everything.

00:24:10.960 --> 00:24:12.210
You must not put yourself in danger

00:24:12.640 --> 00:24:13.690
And worry the Crown Prince.

00:24:14.840 --> 00:24:17.530
I would do anything for you,

00:24:18.880 --> 00:24:19.820
Without a single regret.

00:24:21.340 --> 00:24:22.420
I know your loyalty.

00:24:22.710 --> 00:24:24.050
But this time, you can't help.

00:24:24.470 --> 00:24:25.530
If we don't try,

00:24:26.440 --> 00:24:27.900
How do we know a way won't open up?

00:24:29.400 --> 00:24:30.010
Your Highness,

00:24:30.750 --> 00:24:33.380
Just let me try.

00:24:44.310 --> 00:24:45.490
Time is running out.

00:24:46.440 --> 00:24:47.770
Hand over the Divine Tree now,

00:24:48.310 --> 00:24:51.210
Or don't blame me for resorting to force!

00:24:52.750 --> 00:24:53.580
Sir,

00:24:54.160 --> 00:24:55.530
I don't know where the Divine Tree is.

00:24:55.790 --> 00:24:56.940
Even if it exists,

00:24:57.310 --> 00:24:58.900
It must be with the demons.

00:25:00.550 --> 00:25:01.900
Why are you pushing us so hard?

00:25:19.030 --> 00:25:20.380
The Divine Tree's aura.

00:25:53.920 --> 00:25:54.580
Close your eyes.

00:25:55.750 --> 00:25:56.250
Go!

00:25:57.200 --> 00:25:57.820
Don't run!

00:26:29.990 --> 00:26:31.490
It really is the Divine Tree.

00:26:43.920 --> 00:26:46.140
If you hadn't used the Xuanhua Sacred Fire,

00:26:46.470 --> 00:26:48.290
The Divine Tree wouldn't have been destroyed!

00:26:51.160 --> 00:26:52.900
You're the one who scared them off.

00:26:53.510 --> 00:26:55.580
That black-clad demon must be Zong Quan's accomplice!

00:26:58.510 --> 00:27:00.490
Sir, if you hadn't been pushing so hard,

00:27:00.960 --> 00:27:01.940
Tongzhou would've found

00:27:01.960 --> 00:27:03.690
The Divine Tree that Zong Quan hid in the palace.

00:27:04.200 --> 00:27:05.050
Now we have nothing.

00:27:05.340 --> 00:27:05.860
Outrageous!

00:27:08.440 --> 00:27:09.180
Cuixuan.

00:27:09.790 --> 00:27:11.970
I think Zong Quan's situation is complicated.

00:27:12.200 --> 00:27:13.970
He's practicing evil arts now

00:27:14.200 --> 00:27:16.250
And has ties to the Divine Tree.

00:27:17.030 --> 00:27:17.730
What a pity

00:27:17.880 --> 00:27:18.450
We only got

00:27:18.470 --> 00:27:20.490
A fragment of the Divine Tree.

00:27:21.160 --> 00:27:22.490
Do you think a mere fragment

00:27:22.510 --> 00:27:25.420
Has weaker spirit energy than the whole thing?

00:27:26.340 --> 00:27:27.690
Even if it's just a fragment,

00:27:28.340 --> 00:27:30.010
I need to refine it as soon as possible.

00:27:39.640 --> 00:27:41.730
Where are Jiang Lifei and Lei Xiuyuan?

00:27:47.750 --> 00:27:48.820
Jiang hasn't healed from her injuries.

00:27:49.440 --> 00:27:51.050
Lei has been looking after her.

00:27:52.160 --> 00:27:52.900
How convenient.

00:27:53.470 --> 00:27:54.900
The moment a demon spy appeared,

00:27:55.200 --> 00:27:56.820
Those two vanished.

00:27:57.790 --> 00:27:59.530
Sir, with you and Elder Chongyi here,

00:27:59.840 --> 00:28:01.580
We wouldn't dare overstep.

00:28:02.200 --> 00:28:04.010
We don't want to give anyone more reason to talk.

00:28:04.880 --> 00:28:06.580
Besides, we weren't even there when the demon was chased.

00:28:08.200 --> 00:28:11.730
Right. Lifei was badly hurt this time.

00:28:12.790 --> 00:28:13.730
Perfect.

00:28:14.160 --> 00:28:15.490
I'll go see

00:28:16.100 --> 00:28:17.620
Just how badly hurt she is.

00:28:23.600 --> 00:28:24.180
Mas...

00:28:31.510 --> 00:28:33.970
Lifei, I brought Elder Cuixuan to see you.

00:28:38.710 --> 00:28:39.660
Maybe we should skip it?

00:28:40.100 --> 00:28:40.860
Out of my way!

00:29:01.070 --> 00:29:02.420
How is she? Is she alri...?

00:29:06.510 --> 00:29:07.530
Master.

00:29:11.200 --> 00:29:12.690
What are you two doing?

00:29:21.600 --> 00:29:24.940
Sir, they've been close since their academy days.

00:29:25.840 --> 00:29:28.380
They're in love. Couldn't help themselves.

00:29:29.070 --> 00:29:29.860
It's a good thing!

00:29:30.200 --> 00:29:31.660
Good thing, my foot!

00:29:32.440 --> 00:29:33.730
This brings shame to our sect!

00:29:37.990 --> 00:29:39.290
Never expected Mountain Sect disciples

00:29:40.120 --> 00:29:41.530
To be so passionate.

00:29:42.230 --> 00:29:43.620
Admirable.

00:29:44.310 --> 00:29:46.530
Enough! Don't make things worse.

00:29:50.790 --> 00:29:53.900
No wonder the three of them have such tangled ties.

00:29:54.640 --> 00:29:56.010
The Divine Tree's spirit aura has weakened.

00:29:56.200 --> 00:29:57.820
I need to return and refine it.

00:29:59.920 --> 00:30:01.820
All of you, go back.

00:30:02.120 --> 00:30:03.730
We've had enough embarrassment today.

00:30:04.710 --> 00:30:05.490
Please.

00:30:06.120 --> 00:30:07.860
Save some face for Zhuiyu Peak.

00:30:08.750 --> 00:30:10.180
Just go back. Alright?

00:30:12.360 --> 00:30:13.970
A fine disciple you have.

00:30:16.990 --> 00:30:18.900
I'll leave her to you.

00:30:37.400 --> 00:30:38.340
Pack up.

00:30:39.440 --> 00:30:41.050
Go back to where you belong.

00:30:48.230 --> 00:30:49.820
Exactly. There's always time.

00:30:50.160 --> 00:30:50.900
The elders...

00:30:51.360 --> 00:30:52.730
The elders already know anyway.

00:31:01.030 --> 00:31:01.580
Xiuyuan!

00:31:08.550 --> 00:31:10.660
It's a Fire-Releasing Pill. It neutralizes the Xuanhua Fire toxin.

00:31:20.550 --> 00:31:21.140
Feeling better?

00:31:21.470 --> 00:31:22.210
Feeling any better?

00:31:30.400 --> 00:31:32.250
We'll settle the score for knocking me out later.

00:31:33.120 --> 00:31:34.490
Now take me to the one who posed as me.

00:31:41.310 --> 00:31:41.940
Miaoqing!

00:31:43.200 --> 00:31:44.050
How did this happen?

00:31:47.070 --> 00:31:48.010
I failed to protect her.

00:31:49.200 --> 00:31:51.970
She was badly wounded by a demon spirit and Xuanhua Fire.

00:32:00.160 --> 00:32:01.490
Remember, don't open your eyes.

00:32:31.230 --> 00:32:33.770
I managed to protect her heart meridians, but...

00:32:41.120 --> 00:32:43.100
The Fire-Releasing Pill. Give it to her.

00:32:43.440 --> 00:32:46.620
Her soul has scattered. The pill won't work anymore.

00:32:49.790 --> 00:32:50.530
Let me try.

00:33:13.750 --> 00:33:14.730
Her soul is already lost.

00:33:15.990 --> 00:33:17.180
No amount of spirit power will help.

00:33:23.790 --> 00:33:25.420
But we can't just watch her die.

00:33:28.510 --> 00:33:29.660
I can call her soul back.

00:33:35.710 --> 00:33:36.770
Lifei, stay calm.

00:33:36.790 --> 00:33:37.940
Lu and I will help here.

00:33:38.120 --> 00:33:39.210
You go deal with the elders.

00:33:40.880 --> 00:33:41.380
Do you really have

00:33:41.400 --> 00:33:42.820
A way to bring her soul back?

00:33:44.790 --> 00:33:46.340
Many fishermen in the East Sea go out to sea.

00:33:46.880 --> 00:33:48.580
Strange things happen out there.

00:33:48.990 --> 00:33:50.530
It's not uncommon for souls to go missing out there.

00:33:51.360 --> 00:33:53.100
So there's an ancient soul-calling method in the East Sea.

00:33:54.990 --> 00:33:56.180
But this method

00:33:56.400 --> 00:33:57.580
Comes with a strict condition.

00:33:58.200 --> 00:33:59.900
It requires the person who matters most to her

00:34:00.360 --> 00:34:01.620
To personally call out her name.

00:34:06.640 --> 00:34:07.210
I'll do it.

00:34:40.840 --> 00:34:41.420
Your Highness.

00:34:41.630 --> 00:34:42.170
Miaoqing.

00:34:43.590 --> 00:34:44.170
Miaoqing.

00:34:47.510 --> 00:34:48.300
Your Highness.

00:35:12.700 --> 00:35:13.170
This...

00:35:16.070 --> 00:35:16.860
What do we do?

00:35:17.550 --> 00:35:18.780
How do we ease her pain?

00:35:23.470 --> 00:35:27.050
Miaoqing, I'm here.

00:35:53.190 --> 00:35:54.090
Let me heal her.

00:35:55.470 --> 00:35:56.420
You may all leave.

00:36:05.470 --> 00:36:06.050
Let's go.

00:36:30.320 --> 00:36:30.970
Miaoqing.

00:36:40.880 --> 00:36:43.340
Miaoqing is truly devoted.

00:36:51.700 --> 00:36:52.900
Duanming City's situation is shifting.

00:36:53.220 --> 00:36:53.860
Return at once.

00:36:58.800 --> 00:37:00.650
Lifei, Duanming is unstable.

00:37:01.280 --> 00:37:03.050
Lu and I have to return to Wanxian Sect.

00:37:04.110 --> 00:37:06.450
Take care, everyone. Hope we meet again soon.

00:37:06.990 --> 00:37:07.700
You take care too.

00:37:26.060 --> 00:37:29.740
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

00:37:30.060 --> 00:37:32.560
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

00:37:33.920 --> 00:37:34.490
Lifei!

00:37:34.490 --> 00:37:36.340
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

00:37:36.580 --> 00:37:38.780
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

00:37:39.150 --> 00:37:40.610
Your spirit power isn't limitless.

00:37:41.150 --> 00:37:42.610
If you keep channeling it, you'll collapse.

00:37:44.020 --> 00:37:45.510
♪Love sprouts again in this lifetime♪

00:37:45.510 --> 00:37:47.340
Miaoqing ended up like this because of me.

00:37:48.760 --> 00:37:50.340
I'm the one Cuixuan was after...

00:37:50.360 --> 00:37:51.300
Jiang Lifei!

00:37:52.630 --> 00:37:54.130
You're just like me. Just an ordinary person.

00:37:54.150 --> 00:37:55.220
A mortal.

00:37:55.220 --> 00:37:56.880
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

00:37:56.880 --> 00:37:57.570
But...

00:37:58.590 --> 00:38:00.820
Whatever happened, it's in the past.

00:38:01.700 --> 00:38:02.340
Alright?

00:38:02.340 --> 00:38:04.040
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge. Past the pagoda♪

00:38:04.680 --> 00:38:06.960
♪In fine robes on galloping horses♪

00:38:07.760 --> 00:38:11.240
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

00:38:11.600 --> 00:38:13.880
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

00:38:14.400 --> 00:38:17.360
♪Betrayed by all, I still♪

00:38:17.700 --> 00:38:18.740
Let's go back to Qingqiu together.

00:38:18.740 --> 00:38:20.280
♪Reign supreme♪

00:38:20.670 --> 00:38:21.900
We'll go somewhere no one can find us.

00:38:21.900 --> 00:38:23.590
♪With you, we melt into mist and haze♪

00:38:23.590 --> 00:38:24.340
Just us.

00:38:34.550 --> 00:38:36.130
But I still haven't found my master.

00:38:37.110 --> 00:38:38.340
All this time,

00:38:38.990 --> 00:38:40.650
Not a single word from him.

00:38:41.280 --> 00:38:43.010
And I don't know where Jiaping is.

00:38:43.150 --> 00:38:44.820
Let things take their course. Don't force it.

00:38:46.320 --> 00:38:48.340
Elder Chongyi meant the exact opposite of what he said.

00:38:48.360 --> 00:38:49.490
Don't you get it?

00:38:49.540 --> 00:38:51.890
♪Pierced by countless arrows, pain and illness pile on♪

00:38:51.890 --> 00:38:53.590
♪Yet I remain silent♪

00:38:53.590 --> 00:38:57.700
Lifei, listen to me. Go back to Qingqiu.

00:38:57.700 --> 00:38:59.210
♪Deep love and long yearning, a kiss falls into a dream♪

00:38:59.370 --> 00:39:02.570
♪In the distant night, bitterness blooms♪

00:39:03.360 --> 00:39:05.260
Remember the first time we went back to Qingqiu?

00:39:06.960 --> 00:39:08.260
You said you wanted to build a big house.

00:39:09.990 --> 00:39:10.780
I've already planned it.

00:39:11.590 --> 00:39:13.740
A courtyard with rooms on all sides,

00:39:14.510 --> 00:39:15.340
Filled with flowers

00:39:17.400 --> 00:39:18.570
Blooming all year round.

00:39:20.040 --> 00:39:22.570
♪In fine robes on galloping horses♪

00:39:22.810 --> 00:39:26.670
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

00:39:26.670 --> 00:39:28.010
You said you love radishes.

00:39:29.030 --> 00:39:30.570
We'll plant radishes in the front and back yards.

00:39:30.570 --> 00:39:32.470
♪Betrayed by all, I still♪

00:39:32.470 --> 00:39:33.090
Alright?

00:39:34.080 --> 00:39:36.360
♪Reign supreme♪

00:39:36.930 --> 00:39:40.890
♪If the seal can't be broken, then let it go♪

00:39:41.920 --> 00:39:43.260
Besides radishes,

00:39:43.670 --> 00:39:45.530
We should keep some chickens and ducks too.

00:39:46.190 --> 00:39:47.530
With some meat,

00:39:47.800 --> 00:39:49.090
The stewed radish will taste better.

00:39:51.070 --> 00:39:51.820
Whatever you say.

00:39:51.820 --> 00:39:54.410
♪Always, at the very end of fate♪

00:39:54.650 --> 00:39:57.770
♪Comes that one moment of defiance♪

00:39:57.810 --> 00:40:00.550
♪In the human world or above, like flowing water♪

00:40:00.550 --> 00:40:03.010
With vegetables and meat, once we have it all set up,

00:40:03.320 --> 00:40:04.650
Maybe my master will come back.

00:40:04.650 --> 00:40:08.570
♪Let this fleeting life be whatever it may♪

00:40:16.480 --> 00:40:18.320
[Miniature Realm]

00:40:25.510 --> 00:40:28.860
You hid the Divine Tree by every means possible.

00:40:31.670 --> 00:40:33.530
But I still found it.

00:40:34.920 --> 00:40:35.700
Qingcheng,

00:40:37.360 --> 00:40:39.340
You lost after all.

00:40:41.470 --> 00:40:42.450
Let me see.

00:40:44.110 --> 00:40:44.900
Fine.

00:41:01.550 --> 00:41:02.050
You!

00:41:04.470 --> 00:41:05.940
What have you done?

00:41:08.550 --> 00:41:10.780
Things that shouldn't exist in this world.

00:41:12.220 --> 00:41:13.570
Better to destroy them.

00:41:45.360 --> 00:41:46.260
Qingcheng.

00:41:49.880 --> 00:41:51.420
You forced my hand.

00:41:54.840 --> 00:41:56.130
Gelin and Lu have returned to report.

00:41:57.030 --> 00:41:57.860
We should be going too.

00:42:00.840 --> 00:42:02.380
Tomorrow is Jingwu's coronation.

00:42:03.440 --> 00:42:04.380
Can you stay a little longer?

00:42:04.880 --> 00:42:05.860
If we stay,

00:42:05.990 --> 00:42:07.450
We might just cause you more trouble.

00:42:08.280 --> 00:42:10.570
You have to guide the Crown Prince and restore the Yue State.

00:42:10.880 --> 00:42:12.260
Don't wear yourself out for me.

00:42:13.150 --> 00:42:15.220
Next time we meet, I hope we're all doing well.

00:42:21.280 --> 00:42:22.050
Where are you going?

00:42:30.320 --> 00:42:31.260
We're going...

00:42:33.470 --> 00:42:35.650
Master is at Hushe Peak.

00:42:37.470 --> 00:42:38.780
Jiaping's distant-sensing talisman?

00:42:40.720 --> 00:42:41.740
He's in danger.

00:42:42.050 --> 00:42:42.780
[The Eternal Fragrance]

00:42:42.780 --> 00:42:44.560
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

